# docs/ work notes are local-only by default (plans/specs/reviews/completion
# reports). Already-tracked files are unaffected. Only explicitly curated
# governance docs, executable implementation specs, and docs/protocol/ should be
# re-included below so review-relevant handoff material is not hidden.
/docs/*
!/docs/protocol/
!/docs/engineering-constitution.md
